@page "/"

<PageTitle>Vault · Secure account portal</PageTitle>

<section class="hero">
    <span class="lead-eyebrow">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z" /><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" /></svg>
        Secure account portal
    </span>
    <h1>Sign in once. Your account is always there.</h1>
    <p>
        Vault keeps every account in a SQL Server container backed by a persistent
        volume — so the people you onboard survive each restart, rebuild, and
        redeploy. No reseeding, no lost data, no surprises.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="Account/Register">Create your account</a>
        <a class="btn btn-link btn-lg" href="weather">Explore the demo</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="card-grid" aria-label="What you get">
    <article class="feature-card">
        <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3" /><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5" /><path d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Persistent volume storage</h3>
        <p>Accounts are written to a named volume mounted into SQL Server, so nothing is lost when the container recycles.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card">
        <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z" /><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Secure sign-in</h3>
        <p>Email-confirmed registration, passkey support, and antiforgery-protected forms keep every session locked down.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-card">
        <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2" /><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17" /><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Built on Aspire</h3>
        <p>The portal, database, and persistent volume are wired together and orchestrated by Aspire for a single-command local run.</p>
    </article>
</section>
